<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٤٠ - <span class="c4">[حَدَّثَنَا أَحْمَدُ بْنُ مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ يَعْقُوبَ،]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>عَنْ مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ الْمُبَارَكِ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>بَلَغَنِي أَنَّهُ <span class="c4">[كَانَ نَقْشُ]</span> خَاتَمِ عُثْمَانَ: آمَنَ عُثْمَانُ بِاللَّهِ الْعَظِيمِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>